$interpreted:
Dagger: Ha, ha, ha...
Seriously! What she on? Why does she run so fast?

Dagger: Crap, it's getting dark soon!
Tica! Stop running!
Yan-Bo: "The dust of snow from a hemlock tree. The way sugar shook down on me."
Yan-Bo: Hm, splendid, splendid verse, this is.
Hestia: Yan-Bo, you're doing it again. There isn't even any snow right now.
Pang: Hoo! Haa! HAH!
Puggi: Hearty Hestia~ Wanna go on a date with me~
Puggi: Pang what the ****?!!!!!
Hestia: Hi, Puggi, so you're here. Pang's training right now.
Puggi: Pang why are you training on Christmas no wonder you don't have a girlfriend. Stop training if you keep training you're gonna end up single for life~
Pang: I wouldn't mind that.
Puggi: Pang my man you can't be like that do you want to be that character who wrecks couples everywhere in the Valentine's Day Event Quests every year?
Pang: Sometimes I wonder; is it just me, or is what you are spilling really just nonsense.
Puggi: Whatever man, just listen to me. Stop doing this tedious training and let's have some fun together~
Pang: Appreciate your efforts, but no thanks.
Puggi: Pang why are you so stubborn I won't care about you anymore. When the story concludes don't come to me crying that you don't have a girlfriend.
Tica: Drum roll, please——!
Hestia: Who are you?
Yan-Bo: Young lady, you are?
Tica: I'm Christmas Girl Tica, the one who brings everyone joy and laughter!

Tica: Let's see~ These are your presents! One, two, three...
Exactly the right number!

Tica: I'll be leaving soon~
Today's Christmas; got a full schedule and plenty of places to go~!
Hestia: Yeah! A present~
Hestia: But it seems she forgot about Puggi's share?
Pang: If that fluffball finds out that he's the only one who didn't get a present, he's definitely going to throw a giant tantrum about it.
Dagger: TICA!
Dagger: Just how many people did she give presents to!
Hestia: What... How can he just take my present away like that!
Yan-Bo: Taking without notice, stealing, it is.
Pang: Stealing is an unlawful activity. We must pursue him.
Kittyeyes: You big dumb bear! Stop right there!
Izumi: Yippee~ This is so much fun~ Good thing that I decided to take part in this fiesta~
